Package Monopoly

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • Monopoly.Player
  • public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to instantiate a Player from and keeps track of the player's player num, color, money, properties owned, get out of jail cards, position on board, if they are in jail, distance traveled, and if they can buy a property
